Notes: UCR sophomore center Kemie Nkele ties school career blocked shots record,
recording her 112th. Freshman Seyram Gbewonyo notches career highs of 23
points and 10 rebounds for her first career double-double.
Game.Officials: Kaili Kimura,  Michael Hay,  Joe Ward-Wallace
